      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely thrilled to put this beauty up for grabs! It\u2019s in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels just like it did the day it left the showroom. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure it stayed spotless. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for its next big adventure. If you're looking for something pristine and well-loved, you've found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
