    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of the naturally aspirated S54 inline-six era. The 3.2L power plant features individual throttle bodies and double VANOS, providing a razor-sharp throttle response and a seamless power band to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and an M Variable Differential Lock for superior corner-exit traction. This example is mechanically flawless; the rod bearings have been proactively serviced, and the rear subframe has been reinforced to exceed factory specifications. The suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing OEM bushings and dampers to preserve the legendary BMW M-division handling characteristics. A true collector-grade specimen for the purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
