    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality vehicle that has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with no swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings to speak of, thanks to a professional-grade ceramic coating applied annually. Inside, the cabin still carries that distinctive new-car aroma; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, and the dashboard is free of any sun-fading or micro-scratches. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the adaptive cruise control, functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It features a documented, full-service history performed exclusively by certified technicians using OEM parts. The engine bay is immaculate, the transmission shifts with buttery smoothness, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. Riding on a set of premium tires with near-full tread and flawless alloy wheels, this car drives with the precision and tightness of a brand-new vehicle. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade example for the most discerning buyer.",
      "price": 44900.0,
